creator: Playwaze Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Playwaze makes it easier to organise your sports activities.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Create a community for your team, group, club, or association. Select which activity applets you want to use, invite your members, and get playing!

APPLETS:

* Group Play for running sessions and courses.

* Team Manager for publishing fixtures and managing player availability.

* Quick Play helps your members to organise their own sports activities with each other.

* Leagues, Tournaments, and Ladders allows your players to organise matches and enter results right through the app.

* Progress Pathways for monitoring player development.

* News, Diary, Messaging, and Chat for all your communication needs.

* PlayPay provides an easy way to take payments.

With all your activities in one place Playwaze provides a simple one stop portal into your all your sports group's activities. Makes it easier to organise and more engaging for your members.

With a range of configurable notification options you can be sure that everyone will know who's playing, where they're playing, where they are in the competitions, what courses and sessions are available, when the next match is, and how much they need to pay.

IN-APP UPGRADE:

The Playwaze app can be downloaded for free and you will have full interactive access to all features free for 60 days. The Playwaze website provides full interactive access to all features free at all times.

Once your app's 60 day free trial has expired you can continue using the Playwaze app for free, but you will no longer be able to submit data through it e.g. enter results, post messages, and sign up for fixtures. You'll still be able to see all your activities and you'll continue to receive all your Playwaze notifications.

There are two app upgrade options:
* Monthly priced at £0.79 a month.
* Yearly priced at £5.99 a year.
Both upgrade subscriptions will give you full interactive access to limitless Playwaze communities while the upgrade subscription is active.

Payment will be charged to your Google Play Account at confirmation of purchase.
descriptionShort: Playwaze is a free website & mobile app that makes sport easier to organise.

title: Playwaze

creator: Playwaze
descriptionHtml:
Playwaze is the leading digital platform that makes it easy to organise and participate in your sport and physical activity online and in an app.

Whether you’re a sports club or team, a fitness provider, charity, a regional or national sports organisation, or just a small group of friends, Playwaze has a range of purpose-built features that will make this easier for you.

Simply create your Playwaze community, select the features you need and invite your participants to join. With everything you and they need in one place, online and on their phones, it’s no wonder over 5,000 organisers have Playwaze as their app of choice.

Come discover why, download the Playwaze app today.

Use Playwaze for:

> Your Own Feed: Personalised notifications feed with helpful reminders for both organisers and participants.

> Your Activities: Take registrations and bookings, manage capacity, track attendance and send automatic reminders to attendees.

> Your Memberships: Process your memberships online and via the app.

> Your Competitions: Manage tournaments, leagues, ladders and leaderboards with online and in-app entries and results.

> Your Teams: Manage teams, player availability, squad selection, and match fees.

> Your Challenges: A digital solution for virtual competitions with built-in rewards.
